{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 236.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was the beginning of hell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were all lined up, sick, and old, and people on stretchers out of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had to go to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know where we going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were marched-- traffic was stopped and we marched in the-- on the cen-- on the road, in the center of the road.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the non-Jews were standing around, some smiling, some hiding their smiles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No one was crying, as I can remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not a morsel of sadness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot understand why, but it was that, by itself, the heartlessness, was a brutal experience.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they claimed that they had fears about being punished for showing any kind of sympathy, but I think it goes beyond that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was too much hatred, too much ill will for me to allow for any kind of sentimentality.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was bad, very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remember the good people and the bad people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The good people were the ones who were being exiled and tortured, and the bad ones were the ones who were taking over our homes, and were glad to do so, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't take that many, because the power behind them was so great that-- we didn't have any guns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no way of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] harming them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only they had every way of harming us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is-- I don't remember goodness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know of any family that was hidden by anyone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Though I-- yes, I should amend that by saying that one family who-- who was sent a great deal of money from America was hidden for dollars.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know for how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if they survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
